messages.message:
hi team, i have a pr here https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/71845 failing on the make-sandbox step w/ this msg:
```Fatal: workload "dev": workload is problematic.
Error: Process completed with exit code 1.```
could i get some help figuring out what's going wrong here?

you can ignore the Webpacked Tests / webpacked-tests (pull_request) (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/actions/runs/16119663786/job/45481939382?pr=71845) github action

it's not fully ready yet, so it's not blocking
The webpacked-test failed probably because your branch is more than 50 commits away from `origin/master` . It should be resolved if you try rebasing the latest master
sounds good, will that also fix the make-sandbox issue or is that a separate thing?
ah yep, found the sandbox and see it's the same error as this https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C05L87V014J/p1742338350609229, will try some things listed
